NAME
       sgml2lyx - create LyX output from a SGML source file

SYNOPSIS
       sgml2lyx [generic-option...]  file[.sgml]

DESCRIPTION
       sgml2lyx converts a SGML source file to LyX output. Output
       will appear in file.lyx where file is the name of the SGML
       source file.

       The  attribute/value  pair  "output=lyx" is set for condi­
       tionals.

OPTIONS
       sgm2lyx accepts all the generic options described in sgml­
       tools(1).

       file   The   SGML   source  file,  named  either  file  or
              file.sgml

FILES
       Many files and executables  in  $LINUXDOCLIB  and  $LINUX­
       DOCBIN are used.

BUGS
       None known.

